## Capacity Planning Workflow

- [ ] 1. Inventory resources: List team members, skills, and availability
- [ ] 2. Forecast demand: Estimate hours/story points needed per project
- [ ] 3. Calculate capacity: Compare demand against available hours
- [ ] 4. Identify gaps: Flag over-capacity (burnout risk) or under-capacity (waste)
- [ ] 5. Resolve gaps: Hire, reassign, delay, or scope adjust
- [ ] 6. Monitor: Track actual vs. planned throughout the period

## Key Inputs
- Team: {{team_name}}
- Period: {{planning_period}}
- Committed work: {{committed_work}}
- Available hours: {{available_hours}}
